EXHIBIT B — Cooperative Governance Summary Template

When Cooperative Governance applies, publish a document containing
at minimum:

  1. Governance Structure: How voting rights are organized.
  2. Eligible Voters: How Service Users qualify to vote.
  3. Voting Process: How votes are conducted, counted, and published.
  4. Financial Reports: Where and when financial disclosures are made.
  5. Decision Calendar: How Major Decisions are scheduled and noticed.
  6. Data Export: How Service Users export their data.
  7. Contact: How Service Users can raise governance questions.

